OL,3,CDog walker-turned rioter jailed after
OL,4,Cdragging officer to ground
OL,6,FA 60-year-old dog walker who became
OL,7,Finvolved in rioting in Rotherham has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed after footage showed him
OL,9,Fdragging a police officer to the
OL,10,Fground.
OL,12,FA bodyworn camera recorded Glyn Guest
OL,13,Frepeatedly approaching a line of
OL,14,Foutnumbered police, who were
OL,15,Fprotecting the Holiday Inn Express,
OL,16,Fwhich was being used to house asylum
OL,17,Fseekers.
