OL,6,FIt showed Guest being pushed back five
OL,7,Ftimes before he grabbed the shield of
OL,8,Fanother officer, who was pulled to the
OL,9,Fground to the cheers of the crowd.
OL,11,FThe female officer whose footage was
OL,12,Fplayed said in an impact statement "I
OL,13,Fwas terrified for my safety" during
OL,14,Fthe disorder outside the hotel, during
OL,15,Fwhich more than 50 police were injured
OL,16,Fand there were attempts to storm the
OL,17,Fbuilding and set it alight.
