OL,10,Fyears of service.
OL,12,FChris Aspinall, mitigating, told the
OL,13,Fcourt his client "simply has no
OL,14,Fexplanation for his behaviour".
OL,16,FMr Aspinall said: "He was out walking
OL,17,Fhis dog. He lives about two miles from
OL,18,Fwhere this happened.
