OL,6,FFather-of-three Trevor Lloyd, 49, was
OL,7,Fpart of the mob that stormed the
OL,8,Fhotel, the court heard.
OL,10,FLloyd filmed on a phone as the Holiday
OL,11,FInn Express was breached and then
OL,12,Ffollowed the group of men in through a
OL,13,Fsmashed-in fire door.
OL,15,FJudge Richardson was shown TikTok
OL,16,Ffootage of the crowd breaking in,
OL,17,Fbringing out items including furniture
OL,18,Fand fire extinguishers and then
OL,19,Fthrowing them at a line of police with
OL,20,Friot shields who were forced to
OL,21,Fretreat by the barrage.
